This directory is intended for automated tests and test-related files.

The current project is still focused on embedded bring-up, IMU logging, and storage validation, so there are no PlatformIO tests here yet.

Good future candidates for tests include:
- CSV line formatting logic
- command parsing behavior
- storage statistics calculations
- feature extraction helpers for activity classification

When the firmware grows further, this directory should hold unit or integration tests that can be run with PlatformIO Test Runner.
